caption:
The most successful people I've met:

1. Put Tun on Tv before Watch Television Show
2. Buy Fishing Pole, Go Fishing
3. Understand you can't Study for Subject without Read Literature Upon Subject
4. Intelligence, Entertaining
5. See that Sponges and Paper Towels are Absorbent
6. Put Use Pen before Write Poem
